title: Ebro In The Morning - Vacations + Old Pets + Corny Mayoral Candidates
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 6/14.  

Rosenberg tells us who played themselves (13:45), and Laura Stylez has her patented Flashing Lights segments (9:30, 35:00 & 1:02:00). The Crew opens up the Vacation Disaster Line (41:00) and give some Guru-like advice (51:00).

Please like and subscribe to Ebro In The Morning.
